{"tid":1468273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不割蓆 背後嘅 理論","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:27:08.000Z","uid":18109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d9dbb120fc5984c0d9f3431733302cb907b1451","tid":1468273,"uid":18109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:13:17.000Z","msg":"如果啲人問我<br />\n點解死都不割蓆<br />\n我唸背後問題得一個<br />\n有冇當香港係自己嘅國家<br />\n<br />\n係繁華盛世 <br />\n左同右兩派就一件事打到死係冇問題的<br />\n但而家外敵當前<br />\n我地打緊嘅係<br />\n國家保衛戰 定係 一場運動？<br />\n你地應該好清楚<br />\n<br />\n不過咁<br />\n一個國家會唔會有黑暗野？<br />\n你話呢？<br />\n但佢地係點樣包裝??<br />\n你想要咩方式，點樣先係最靚<br />\n係文化嘅問題<br />\n呢啲係有得傾嘅<br />\n小事<br />\n<br />\n大事<br />\n最重要最重要<br />\n大家要唸<br />\n我地最終嘅目標係乜？<br />\n肯定答你<br />\n五。大。訴。求"},{"pid":"35dc741ead135e29c14592dcb1f4fd9b4e007d8b","tid":1468273,"uid":18109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:14:10.000Z","msg":"你地不割蓆嘅原因又係乜？"},{"pid":"e5e8fc844ff29383246225d68d3ec75f37ea5e80","tid":1468273,"uid":94538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:15:14.000Z","msg":"814照入機場，但和理非主場，道歉+幫旅客+文宣！<br />\n<br />\n[推！！！ 道歉是必須] 話錯既係政府，洗乜撚野道歉既入<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467612</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ced8b0d868d010d7bb854bc8d5c85809e1776d15","tid":1468273,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1FNfTAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1FNfTAU.jpg&h=7becab2d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E9TyFfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE9TyFfU.jpg&h=0b41b5ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8shGO9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8shGO9f.jpg&h=e0856b12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae92dcfed0690853154e230b9e76aa1e0f6f4282","tid":1468273,"uid":22047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:17:18.000Z","msg":"我認為呢次係香港保衛戰。唔係俾泛民左膠收割選票嘅運動。所以張超雄之流係阻礙呢場戰役嘅一粒大釘。"},{"pid":"90897db3087e4b350b4f05b20419e01363e3e432","tid":1468273,"uid":266203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:18:11.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GVtrfTe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGVtrfTe.jpg&h=32eb9a6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BNJVTES.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBNJVTES.jpg&h=070ec636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SuBgC6v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSuBgC6v.jpg&h=4e21a231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EesWC6u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEesWC6u.jpg&h=4d3f45a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZumsKMJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZumsKMJ.jpg&h=27bef57f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OAFM0j4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOAFM0j4.jpg&h=40332d8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/skJSbrL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FskJSbrL.jpg&h=64f74bb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">free to print : <a href=\"https://we.tl/t-zTHYn0SbVd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwe.tl%2Ft-zTHYn0SbVd&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=ef8148f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://we.tl/t-zTHYn0SbVd</a></span>"},{"pid":"8167b38c3799ed8ce52ac5dc9e32743cbf22332d","tid":1468273,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:27:08.000Z","msg":"不割席 不分化 兄弟爬山<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">弱點已經比敵人對準！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n只要搵幾條仆街帶風就已經成功破解我哋呢三句格言！！<br />\n<br />\n不割不分吖嘛！！<br />\n搵人帶風自然有人跟！！<br />\n搵鬼落場做乜嘢都可以入你數！<br />\n<br />\n再唔諗辦法<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">捉鬼</span></strong>，我哋真係死撚硬！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">兄弟不割，鬼同分化撚一定要割</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n要有效捉鬼，前線一定要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有底線共識</span></strong>，咩可以做，咩唔可以做，一過底線就係鬼，即捉！唔係割席，唔係分化呀！係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">認真解決問題呀！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n分化同鬼從來都係狗共致勝之道<br />\n，要對付唯一方法就係<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">團結</span></strong></strong>！！<br />\n既然團結，就嘗試傾個底線共識，唔係所有野要有共識，底線真係有須要呀！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一定捉鬼呀！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">底線共識大家可以討論</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大前提係畀全世界知我哋係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">為自由良知而戰嘅正義之師，係保護市民嘅黑衣人！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1.可以打遊擊同快閃， 唔放火/唔掉磚/唔衝/唔主動出手/唔傷及無無辜。<br />\n<br />\n2. 可以佔路set路障，圍，口撩，還拖！但不主動出擊，不傷及無辜。<br />\n<br />\n3.不送頭，所有可以被聯上暴動同暴徒嘅，都唔好做。<br />\n<br />\n4. 贏輿論同民心唔係講緊連登呀！自high有乜撚嘢用！<br />\n<br />\n輿論係正常媒體包括 social media 同埋國際輿論，民心唔使講啦！<br />\n<br />\n失民心同輿論，話撚知你連登幾high幾高漲，大家可以返屋企含撚啦！<br />\n<br />\n輿論同民心係要嚟令對家喺國際/同社會有壓力！<br />\n<br />\n只要set到個底線嘅共識， <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我哋先可以真正團結，<strong><strong></strong></strong>先有機會贏</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁我先真正做到<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">兄弟爬山 不割席 不分化！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁多位手足認真諗諗啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}